In the Matter of MARLINROX, LIMITED, a Corporation, Bankrupt. O. T. GILBANK, Trustee in Bankruptcy of Marlinrox, Ltd., Appellant, v. E. E. McGILL, as Receiver, Appellee. No. 8216. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit. June 1, 1936. Hiram E. Casey, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellant. James C. Ingebretsen, of Los Angeles, Cal., for appellee.

Before WILBUR, GARRECHT, and DENMAN, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Upon stipulation of counsel for respective parties, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith.
